title: [Ta'Illistim, Rocky Trail]
description: Small rocks are scattered across the trail before it turns up the mountain.  A series of evergreens line the trail up to the foot of the mountain.  An onyx obelisk stands as a silent sentinel at the base of the mountain.  Moonbeams seem to focus on the obelisk.
